"{\"uid\": \"kbzk.com-news-local-news-manhattan-marksman-returns-from-2024-paris-olympics-determined-to-compete-again\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"MANHATTAN - Sergeant Ivan Roe is a Manhattan native and renowned marksman-and now, an Olympian, as he returns home from the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.8720685860383645, \"rank\": 0.14669879414344736, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 94, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999790298557008, \"rank\": 2.0875631159220776e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sergeant Ivan Roe\", \"from\": 12, \"to\": 29}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Knowing that I was going after having come so close twice before-it was like a huge weight off my shoulders.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge weight\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"my shoulders\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like it felt like I had been cursed and it was finally over,\\\" says Sgt.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sgt\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe began shooting when he was only seven years old after his father enrolled him in a BB-gun program.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"a BB-gun program\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says, \\\"I had no intention to go to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no intention\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not even know it as an Olympic sport.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was shooting BB-guns and just having fun with my friends.\\\"\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"BB-guns\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"my friends\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Sgt.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sgt\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe began competing at an international level in high school, he enlisted in the military after graduation, joining the Army Marksmanship Unit.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army_Marksmanship_Unit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Army Marksmanship Unit\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army_Marksmanship_Unit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army_Marksmanship_Unit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"an international level\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"the military\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"graduation\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He qualified as an Olympic alternate two times before, finally getting the chance to compete in 2024.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic alternate\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Knowing that I qualified for the Olympics next to people who have won all these medals, who are huge, famous names-it's a good feeling.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"all these medals\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"huge, famous names\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"a good feeling\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard to put into words,\\\" says Sgt.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"Sgt\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says becoming an Olympic competitor was hard to process-and it wasn't until arriving in Paris that all the emotions of competing hit him.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999962821992529, \"rank\": 3.717814634408581e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic competitor\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"all the emotions\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I sat down for the first competition, the mixed team air rifle, I sat behind my point and just kind of got overwhelmed with the emotions and I just sat and cried for probably five minutes before the match started.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first competition\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"my point\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"probably five minutes\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am gonna be honest, it was a mess of a match.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mess\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"a match\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried my best, but it was not pretty,\\\" Roe says.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going forward, Roe says he handled the following competitions well.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"the following competitions\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite not placing how he hoped, took home valuable perspective for the future.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"valuable perspective\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Probably one of the biggest takeaways from Paris was that I am good enough to compete with all these people.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999962821992529, \"rank\": 3.717814634408581e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest takeaways\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"all these people\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were a lot of times in the last four years leading up to the Olympics where I was one of the best in the country-but I did not think I was one of the best in the world,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"the last four years\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sgt.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sgt\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe plans to reenlist for another 4 years with the Army to refine his skills with the new goal of winning an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\", \"score\": 0.999999968944167, \"rank\": 2.4647688916469542e-08, \"text\": \"Army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Army\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"another 4 years\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"his skills\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"the new goal\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says, \\\"I know I made mistakes that I should not have, and I know I can fix those.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mistakes\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if I had not made those mistakes, I know I would have been in the final.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those mistakes\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, moving forward, I am going to correct those mistakes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those mistakes\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roe says he hopes his story can be a message of hope to others coming from small Montana towns.\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2381, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Small_Montana\", \"score\": 0.9999999997703526, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"small Montana\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Small_Montana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Small_Montana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"his story\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would really hope that I could inspire some kid here who thinks that maybe they do not have what it takes, but they want to make a shot at it-to pursue whatever dream they have.\\\"\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some kid\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever dream\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More from MTN News John Riley Madelyn Heath John Riley Q2 News Zach Volheim Jonathon Ambarian Charlie Klepps Mack Carmack\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2729, \"ent